<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>COUNTYOUR BLESSINGS</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Damsung buoina huihpi'n a hun tawh laiin,
 Lungdawnga a manga na kingaih laiin;
 Vangpiekna na chante khat khat in sim in,
 Lalpa'n thil A bawl chuh maksa tei inla.

[V2]
 Vangpiekna chuh khat khat in sim in,
 Vangpiekna Lalpa thilbawl sim in;
 Na vangpiekna khat khat in sim in,
 Lalpa'n thil A bawl chuh maksa tei inla.

[V3]
 2. Damsung thil ngaihtuohna'n a hun subuoi em?
 Nangmah put ding kross chu gik taluo'n na he'm?
 Vangpieknate sim in, ginlahna bei ding,
 Tichun nicheng in nawp la sa thei inla.

[V4]
 3. Midang lopina leh thilneih na et tieng,
 Krista tiem neihzawhna simsenloh gelin;
 Sum a chawk guolloh, vangsakna chuh gelin,
 Van a kipahman leh na In lopi chuh.

[V5]
 4. Tichun, thepna lien leh aneu lak ale,
 Lungdawng ki'n, Pathien in hun panpih ina;
 Vangsakna gelin, Angel in hun veng ding,
 Na zinna ah hun veng in, lungmuon ina.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>24</hymn_number>
</song>